				<wikidot:authorName>Doctor Cimmerian</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1414765</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Guttenberg, New Jersey is, despite a relatively low total population, the most densely populated city in America. Guttenberg is also on the Hudson inside the greater New York Metropolitan area. Guttenberg is, essentially, the most densely populated part of one of the most densely populated regions in the world.</p> <p>There is absolutely no way to evacuate the whole city without prohibitively high costs with regards to amnestics and infosec or a broken masquerade.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
