					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't know how you came up with this, or why, but it's brilliant. The kind of &quot;just a weird thing with no story&quot; that other authors should try to aim for. My only complaint is that halfway through I had an overwhelming urge to shut my eyes and never, ever open them, which hindered my enjoyment of the rest of the article as I could no longer see the page. Aside from that, amazing work :P</p> 
				 	]]>
