					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5842825#post-3791246</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5842825/scp-3316#post-3791246</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 May 2018 13:59:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>fieldstone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1436137</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Eyes can take a pretty incredible beating without rupturing, so it makes sense that they'd be able to squeeze themselves way out of shape to get under doors or through cracks. That might be why they come back so red.</p> <p>I have to say I also really like the image of an eyeball just squirming around a living room all night like a bug in a jar, looking for an escape route.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
